<L>__{interior wyatt club steam room day}
<A>__{gekko and bud sit alone, wreathed in steam.}
<C>__{bud}
<P>__{(sweating)}
<D>__{nice club, mr. gekko...}
<C>__{gekko}
<D>__{yeah... not bad for a city college boy. bought my way into this club and now every one of these ivy league schmucks is sucking my kneecaps...i just got on the board of the zoological society, cost me a million; that's the thing with wasps they like animals but they can't stand people!}
<C>__{bud}
<P>__{(easing into it)}
<D>__{uh, mr. gekko, we took a little loss today. we got stopped out on tarafly...}
<P>__{(gekko waits)}
<D>__{...about 50 thousand.}
<A>__{gekko's expression is frightening but cool.}
<C>__{gekko}
<D>__{i guess your father's not a union representative on that company.}
<C>__{bud}
<P>__{(laughs, shocked)}
<D>__{what? how do you know about my father?}
<C>__{gekko}
<D>__{the most valuable commodity i know of is information. wouldn't you agree on that?}
<C>__{bud}
<P>__{(exhaling deeply)}
<D>__{yes...}
